WEBVTT

1
00:11:00.880 --> 00:11:03.920 
我奶奶秘传的炖牛肉
Grandma Chinkski's pot roast.

2
00:11:03.920 --> 00:11:05.370 
看起来好好吃
This looks amazing.

3
00:11:05.370 --> 00:11:07.150 
我冬天时最喜欢吃根菜类植物了
I love a root vegetable in the winter.

4
00:11:07.150 --> 00:11:13.280 
就不能有一刻不抢我风头吗
Can it ever just be about me?

5
00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:16.960 
* 牛  牛  牛 *
* Beef, beef, beef *

6
00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:19.780 
* 牛肉  牛  牛 *
* B-beef, b-beef, beef *

7
00:11:19.780 --> 00:11:22.530 
干嘛  这是我的牛肉之歌
What? That's my beef song.

8
00:11:24.370 --> 00:11:27.500 
我想对苏菲说几句敬酒词
I'd like to make a toast to Sophie.

9
00:11:27.500 --> 00:11:29.260 
真贴心
Oh, that's sweet.

10
00:11:29.260 --> 00:11:30.870 
但不许敲那杯子
But not with that glass.

11
00:11:30.870 --> 00:11:33.620 
那是我奶奶的水晶杯
That's Grandma Chinski's crystal.

